{
  "texts": [
    "Specifically, for example, for Llama 70B model, we utilized the Llama-2-70B-chat-GPTQ 32 obtained from the Hugging face 33 due to the reduced size, instead of its the standard version.",
    "For the Llama-2-70B-chat-GPTQ, the GPTQ algorithm 34, was employed to quantize Llama 2 models within AutoGPTQ library.",
    "Currently, we have access to only 160 documents from Colorado and Pennsylvania.",
    "This small dataset allowed us to quickly validate our approach.",
    "Once a larger dataset becomes available, the developed framework is expected to scale easily for information extraction."
  ]
}